@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor Black
  LifeLineBorderColor Black
  LifeLineBackgroundColor White
  ParticipantBorderColor Black
  ParticipantBackgroundColor White
  ActorBorderColor Black
  ActorBackgroundColor White
  ParticipantFontColor Black
  ActorFontColor Black
}

actor "User" as User
participant "Frontend" as UI
participant "Backend API\nGET /api/wallets/:walletId/transactions" as API
participant "Database\nTable: Transaction" as DB
User->UI: Open wallet transaction history
UI->API: Request wallet transactions
API->DB: Retrieve wallet transactions
DB-->API: Return transaction records
API-->UI: Return transaction list
UI-->User: Display wallet transaction history

@enduml
